Gentlewoman had a Bastard before she was married.

I humbly beseech you sweet Madam, that my earnest and hearty sorrow may procure remission 
for my inconsiderate and causeless Invectives. Let my confession seem satisfactory, 
and my contrition win indulgency to my forgetful delinquency. I pray you let us kiss and be friends.

Pretty I confess. But that is not the song must do it; 
